tags.name: aframe-player
tags.description:
`aframe-player`
`A wrapper to do data binding into aframe`

Attributes:

  * `source` {`string`} - Source to reference for the 3D object

  * `height` {`string`} - height of the element

  * `width` {`string`} - width of the element

  * `sky-color` {`string`} - Color of the sky / background.

  * `ar` {`boolean`} - If this is for augmented reality or not.

  * `x` {`string`} - x position for the AR element.

  * `y` {`string`} - y position for the AR element.

  * `z` {`string`} - z position for the AR element.

  * `position` - Generate a position object when coordinates change.

  * `schemaMap` - Schema Map for the element, used to generate a valid prefix on the fly
Props set for Polymer compatibility
